Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 02 of Head MRI
When I select 'Motor deficit' from 'Previous interventions/therapies' dropdown menu
Then 'Add clinic' button is enabled
And 'Apraxia' radio button is enabled
And 'Hemiparesis' radio button is enabled
And 'Hemiplegia' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Hemiparesis' radio button
Then 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled
And 'Brachiofacial' radio button is enabled
And 'Lower limb' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Hemiplegia' radio button
Then 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled
And 'Brachiofacial' radio button is enabled
And 'Lower limb' radio button is enabled
